content:
This a test of some markdown possibilities: 

- - -

## Headings

# h1 Heading 1

## h2 Heading 2

### h3 Heading 3

#### h4 Heading 4

##### h5 Heading 5

###### h6 Heading 6

- - -

## Emphasis

**This is bold text**

*This is italic text*

~~Strikethrough~~

- - -

## Links

[link text](https://nexus-dock.github.io/)

- - -

## Blockquotes

> Blockquotes can be nested...
>
> > ...by using additional greater-than signs right next to each other...
> >
> > > ...or with spaces between arrows.

- - -

## Lists

### Unordered

* Create 
* a list 
* by starting 
* a line 
* with `+`, `-`, or `*`

### Ordered

1. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet
2. Consectetur adipiscing elit
3. Integer molestie lorem at massa

- - -

## Images

![Test image](/media/test-image.gif)

- - -

## Code

Inline `code`

Block code "fences"

```
Sample text here...
```

- - -

## Tables

| Option | Description                                                               |
| ------ | ------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| data   | path to data files to supply the data that will be passed into templates. |
| engine | engine to be used for processing templates. Handlebars is the default.    |
| ext    | extension to be used for dest files.                                      |
